#[sub]             has no scriptable observables; assertions land in
#[sub]             m3 once view-toggle bool state or undo-stack depth
#[sub]             gain scriptable surfaces).
#[sub] - 2 error : Phases 7 and 8 — intentional refusals (unknown
#[sub]             verb, extra arguments).
#[sub] - 1 operator-visual : Phase 1's `list` output block (multi-
#[sub]             line; counted as one trace line for the summary).
#[sub] - 5 operator-visual `ok` echoes : Phases 2-6, one per wrapped
#[sub]             verb's successful invocation.
#[sub] - 2 operator-visual refusal lines : the structured
#[sub]             `error invoke threw:` lines under Phases 7 and 8.
#[sub]
