#[sub] Smokes 49 / 50 / 51 each landed 8 pass on their respective
#[sub] format-verbs because those Scriptables had observables
#[sub] (last_ok / last_path); m1's first batch doesn't, so the line
#[sub] count moves to the trace channel and the visual channel.
#[sub]
#[sub] Tier 2 row ticks 0/49 → 5/49 after this smoke lands. Headline %
#[sub] moves from ~75% to ~76% — small step, but the first non-zero
